mail.title: New User Benefits
mail.message:
Welcome, new player!
To thank you for playing LET IT DIE,
here are some presents from us:

KAMAS-A1 Assault Rifle(Blueprint)
Death Metal x20
200,000 Kill Coins
Golden Bird x5
Express 1 Day Pass x5
Skill decal Vampire
Skill decal One Shot One Kill
Skill decal Barbarian

Materials required for the R&D of
assault rifles can be obtained by searching
(2F) WANOKI, (4F) TAGAHARA, (7F) DANEDA
and various floors above the 11th Floor.

*Please collect the items from the Rewards Box.
